<h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
<p>Here you can find answers to some of the most frequently asked questions about our services:</p>

<div class="faq-section">
    <h4>How do I add new products to the inventory?</h4>
    <p>To add new products, navigate to the "Products" section from the main menu and click "Add Product." Fill in the product details and click "Save" to add it to your inventory.</p>

    <h4>Can I generate reports for specific dates?</h4>
    <p>Yes, you can filter reports based on date ranges to see transactions, sales, and inventory data for specific periods. This feature is available under the "Reports" section.</p>

    <h4>How do I track product sales?</h4>
    <p>The "Transactions" section allows you to view all sales made, along with the product details, dates, and amounts. You can filter transactions by product or date for better tracking.</p>
</div>
